Class Patient

java.lang.Object
other.Person

public class Patient extends Person
This class represents a Patient, which extends the Person class. A Patient has a profile and a linked list of visits.

  • Method Details

    • addVisit

      public void addVisit(Visit newVisit)
      Adds a new visit to the patient's list of visits. This method maintains a linked list of visits, ensuring that the most recent visit is added at the end of the list.
      Parameters:
      newVisit - The visit to be added. If it's the first visit, it will be set as the head of the list. If there are existing visits, it will be appended at the end.
